snippet.title: Sunray OS - Trailer (mystery horror game set in a computer)
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2777780/Sunray_OS/

You just bought a PC, only to discover it once belonged to someone who has mysteriously disappeared. You soon realize that the key to find him may be hidden deep inside your OS, governed by a weird AI chatbot named Zippy. What will be your first move?
